<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="bg-soft">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head center"><span class="eyebrow">What we care about</span><h2>The things we will not compromise on</h2></div>
    <div class="values">
      <div class="value">
        <div class="v-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 6l9-3 9 3M5 10v8a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-8M3 6l9 4 9-4"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Fairness first</h4>
        <p>The point of ePegboard is balanced games and a fair share of court time for everyone present. If a change makes the games less fair, it does not ship.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <div class="v-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13A4 4 0 0 1 16 11"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Built from real club nights</h4>
        <p>We design around how sessions actually run - drop-ins, late changes, mixed abilities - and improve off the back of real feedback, not a spec on a whiteboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value">
        <div class="v-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.5 8-8 10-4.5-2-8-5-8-10V6z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <h4>Your data stays yours</h4>
        <p>Your members, results and history belong to your club. Export to CSV whenever you like - nothing is locked in, and the numbers are always yours to take.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

